main event: Observers spotted a white colored object at Willow Grove NAS that disappeared and then reappeared, lasting for 3 minutes.
interesting points: The object was observed by military personnel,The object did not resemble any known aircraft the observers were familiar with,The observers were surprised as they had never seen anything like it before, The object was luminous and moved behind and in front of stars, The object reportedly emitted no sound.
witness description: military personnel who had seen aircraft before
